{
  "video_id": "setJXT-K2CQ",
  "title": "Why Bluefin Tuna Is So Expensive | So Expensive",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 4520.0,
      "end_time": 8350.0,
      "text": "Narrator: In 2013, a 489-pound tuna sold"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 8350.0,
      "end_time": 11600.0,
      "text": "for a whopping $1.8 million."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 11600.0,
      "end_time": 13490.0,
      "text": "But you can buy a can of tuna fish"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 13500.0,
      "end_time": 14793.0,
      "text": "at the grocery store for under $2."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 15870.0,
      "end_time": 17759.0,
      "text": "So, what's the difference?"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 17760.0,
      "end_time": 20400.0,
      "text": "For starters, it's not the same fish."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 20400.0,
      "end_time": 22849.0,
      "text": "Canned tuna typically comes from albacore."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 22850.0,
      "end_time": 26500.0,
      "text": "They're small, grow fast, and are abundant for fishing."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 26500.0,
      "end_time": 29670.0,
      "text": "And they certainly don't weigh 489 pounds."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 29670.0,
      "end_time": 31870.0,
      "text": "There's only one type of tuna in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 31870.0,
      "end_time": 34890.0,
      "text": "that grows that big, bluefin tuna."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 34890.0,
      "end_time": 37350.0,
      "text": "And if you wanna try some, it's gonna cost you."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 37350.0,
      "end_time": 39425.0,
      "text": "Derek Wilcox: We could buy tuna from Japan"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 39425.0,
      "end_time": 40291.0,
      "text": "that we'd have to charge"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 40300.0,
      "end_time": 44309.0,
      "text": "maybe $80 for one piece of otoro."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 44310.0,
      "end_time": 46980.0,
      "text": "Narrator: Derek Wilcox is a chef at Shoji,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 46980.0,
      "end_time": 48970.0,
      "text": "a Japanese restaurant in New York."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 48970.0,
      "end_time": 51190.0,
      "text": "He was trained in Japan and worked there"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 51200.0,
      "end_time": 52420.0,
      "text": "for more than 10 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 52420.0,
      "end_time": 55850.0,
      "text": "Restaurants like Shoji serve raw bluefin tuna,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 55850.0,
      "end_time": 59240.0,
      "text": "or what's called kuro maguro in Japanese."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 59240.0,
      "end_time": 61760.0,
      "text": "They get their tuna from a number of different sources,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 61760.0,
      "end_time": 64670.0,
      "text": "including Japan's Tsukiji fish market."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 64670.0,
      "end_time": 67280.0,
      "text": "There are several different varieties of tuna,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 67280.0,
      "end_time": 69430.0,
      "text": "but bluefin is what you're most likely to find"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 69430.0,
      "end_time": 71100.0,
      "text": "at high-end sushi restaurants."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 71100.0,
      "end_time": 72649.0,
      "text": "Wilcox: Bluefin is the most sought after."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 72650.0,
      "end_time": 76563.0,
      "text": "Only bluefin has the intense marbling."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 78330.0,
      "end_time": 82000.0,
      "text": "Bluefin also, when it's aged properly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 82000.0,
      "end_time": 86300.0,
      "text": "has a particular balance of flavors."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 86300.0,
      "end_time": 87950.0,
      "text": "Narrator: A large adult bluefin can weigh"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 87950.0,
      "end_time": 90370.0,
      "text": "around 450 pounds or more,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 90370.0,
      "end_time": 92350.0,
      "text": "and the price of the fish varies based"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 92350.0,
      "end_time": 94590.0,
      "text": "on a number of different factors."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 94600.0,
      "end_time": 96250.0,
      "text": "Wilcox: It completely depends upon where you get it from,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 96250.0,
      "end_time": 98680.0,
      "text": "but it's never cheap."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 98680.0,
      "end_time": 101470.0,
      "text": "A local bluefin on the east coast will run"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 101470.0,
      "end_time": 104804.0,
      "text": "anywhere between $20 and $40 a pound."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 104804.0,
      "end_time": 109700.0,
      "text": "You could be paying north of $200 a pound"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 109700.0,
      "end_time": 111830.0,
      "text": "for bluefin from Japan."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 111830.0,
      "end_time": 114200.0,
      "text": "Narrator: According to Wilcox, tuna from Japan"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 114200.0,
      "end_time": 115970.0,
      "text": "is better than American tuna during"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 115970.0,
      "end_time": 117340.0,
      "text": "the peak winter months."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 117340.0,
      "end_time": 120300.0,
      "text": "While Boston tuna is best during summer and fall."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 120300.0,
      "end_time": 123200.0,
      "text": "But it's the tuna that comes from Oma in Japan"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 123200.0,
      "end_time": 124270.0,
      "text": "that's widely considered to be"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 124270.0,
      "end_time": 126399.0,
      "text": "some of the best in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 126400.0,
      "end_time": 130480.0,
      "text": "Wilcox: Peak-season Oma tuna will, in Japan, cost"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 130479.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133268.0,
      "text": "400-450 a kilo."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 133269.0,
      "end_time": 135580.0,
      "text": "Which means by the time it gets here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 135580.0,
      "end_time": 137620.0,
      "text": "it'll cost close to $400 a pound."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 137620.0,
      "end_time": 140220.0,
      "text": "Narrator: Besides its superior fat content,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 140220.0,
      "end_time": 142800.0,
      "text": "another reason fish is more expensive from Japan"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 142800.0,
      "end_time": 144500.0,
      "text": "is that it has further to travel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 144500.0,
      "end_time": 146610.0,
      "text": "and it goes through a rather lengthy process"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 146610.0,
      "end_time": 148838.0,
      "text": "before making its way to your plate."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 148838.0,
      "end_time": 151549.0,
      "text": "Wilcox: There's more hands that it passes through"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 151550.0,
      "end_time": 153860.0,
      "text": "in Japan, which is not necessarily a bad thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 153860.0,
      "end_time": 156100.0,
      "text": "Narrator: Wilcox says the fish is also handled"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 156100.0,
      "end_time": 158340.0,
      "text": "better in Japan than the US."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 158340.0,
      "end_time": 161327.0,
      "text": "So there's less damage and more precise cutting."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 161327.0,
      "end_time": 164380.0,
      "text": "Wilcox: We get like a Boston bluefin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 164380.0,
      "end_time": 168730.0,
      "text": "it goes from the fisherman, to the distributor, to our door."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 168730.0,
      "end_time": 171100.0,
      "text": "Whereas in Japan, it's going from the fisherman,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 171100.0,
      "end_time": 175549.0,
      "text": "usually to a collective or cooperative,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 175550.0,
      "end_time": 178470.0,
      "text": "to the government that's running the auction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 178470.0,
      "end_time": 183000.0,
      "text": "to a middle wholesaler, to a final wholesaler,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 183000.0,
      "end_time": 186400.0,
      "text": "to a restaurant or a hotel."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 186400.0,
      "end_time": 188530.0,
      "text": "All high-end fish are auctioned in Japan."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 188530.0,
      "end_time": 190920.0,
      "text": "Fish that's more sought after, that's caught"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 190920.0,
      "end_time": 193490.0,
      "text": "in a better place, that's handled better,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 193500.0,
      "end_time": 196240.0,
      "text": "that's clearly better quality will go for a higher price,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 196240.0,
      "end_time": 199490.0,
      "text": "and that fisherman will get more of the money."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 199490.0,
      "end_time": 201400.0,
      "text": "Narrator: The first auction of the year in Japan"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 201400.0,
      "end_time": 205400.0,
      "text": "is when you'll see ridiculously high prices for fish."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 205400.0,
      "end_time": 208790.0,
      "text": "Mostly as a symbolic gesture, or a publicity stunt."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 208790.0,
      "end_time": 211799.0,
      "text": "Which is partly why the 489-pound tuna sold"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 211800.0,
      "end_time": 215710.0,
      "text": "for $1.8 million in 2013."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 215710.0,
      "end_time": 220330.0,
      "text": "And the first fish of 2018 sold for $323,000."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 220330.0,
      "end_time": 221938.0,
      "text": "Wilcox: In Japanese culture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 221938.0,
      "end_time": 224710.0,
      "text": "that first thing you do all year"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 224710.0,
      "end_time": 225220.0,
      "text": "is the most important."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 225220.0,
      "end_time": 226810.0,
      "text": "It sets the tone for the whole year."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 226810.0,
      "end_time": 229960.0,
      "text": "That first tuna of the year always goes for"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 229960.0,
      "end_time": 231620.0,
      "text": "the highest price that any tuna will"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 231620.0,
      "end_time": 233390.0,
      "text": "go for the whole rest of the year."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 233390.0,
      "end_time": 235529.0,
      "text": "Narrator: And the different parts of a bluefin tuna"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 235530.0,
      "end_time": 237670.0,
      "text": "also vary drastically in price."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 237670.0,
      "end_time": 240799.0,
      "text": "Wilcox: If you imagine a tuna as like a torpedo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 240800.0,
      "end_time": 242480.0,
      "text": "they'll split it into quarters lengthwise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 242480.0,
      "end_time": 244730.0,
      "text": "cut off the head, and the collar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 244730.0,
      "end_time": 247489.0,
      "text": "and we will take one of the two belly quarters."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 247490.0,
      "end_time": 249500.0,
      "text": "Narrator: Here's what one quarter looks like"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 249500.0,
      "end_time": 250520.0,
      "text": "when it's delivered."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 250520.0,
      "end_time": 252300.0,
      "text": "This piece came from Boston,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 252300.0,
      "end_time": 253990.0,
      "text": "and was caught the previous day."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 253990.0,
      "end_time": 256829.0,
      "text": "Wilcox splits up the meat based on type."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 256829.0,
      "end_time": 258630.0,
      "text": "Wilcox: It's just like sides of beef."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 258630.0,
      "end_time": 261790.0,
      "text": "You know, you buy a side of beef, it's all the same,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 261790.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262370.0,
      "text": "but once you break it down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 262370.0,
      "end_time": 264510.0,
      "text": "the filet ends up being the most expensive part,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 264510.0,
      "end_time": 266510.0,
      "text": "because it's the most desirable."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 266510.0,
      "end_time": 267710.0,
      "text": "It's also small,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 267710.0,
      "end_time": 270600.0,
      "text": "and it requires a lot of labor to peel"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 270600.0,
      "end_time": 270893.0,
      "text": "off the silver skin."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 270893.0,
      "end_time": 275104.0,
      "text": "Otoro is the fattiest part of the tuna"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 275855.0,
      "end_time": 278370.0,
      "text": "outside of the head and collar area."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 278370.0,
      "end_time": 280480.0,
      "text": "Narrator: This is the most expensive."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 280480.0,
      "end_time": 281790.0,
      "text": "And depending on where it's from,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 281790.0,
      "end_time": 283620.0,
      "text": "and where the fish was raised,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 283620.0,
      "end_time": 286400.0,
      "text": "the price can vary anywhere from $10 a piece"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 286400.0,
      "end_time": 288460.0,
      "text": "to upwards of $80."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 288460.0,
      "end_time": 290330.0,
      "text": "Wilcox: The chutoro is getting around toward"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 290330.0,
      "end_time": 292745.0,
      "text": "the side of the tuna,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 292745.0,
      "end_time": 296870.0,
      "text": "and it doesn't have the striations of fat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 296870.0,
      "end_time": 301290.0,
      "text": "but it still has fat within the red of the meat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 301290.0,
      "end_time": 303720.0,
      "text": "so you get a mix of fat and red."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 303720.0,
      "end_time": 305760.0,
      "text": "And then, akami which means, literally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 305760.0,
      "end_time": 308330.0,
      "text": "red meat in Japanese,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 308330.0,
      "end_time": 311479.0,
      "text": "is the leanest part which you find more towards the center"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 311480.0,
      "end_time": 313850.0,
      "text": "of the tuna closer to the backbone."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 313850.0,
      "end_time": 315150.0,
      "text": "Narrator: Akami is the most common"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 315150.0,
      "end_time": 316750.0,
      "text": "and cheapest part of the fish,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 316750.0,
      "end_time": 318280.0,
      "text": "but it's still more expensive than"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 318280.0,
      "end_time": 320770.0,
      "text": "that can of albacore at your local market."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 320770.0,
      "end_time": 323440.0,
      "text": "Wilcox: When you're assessing the quality of the tuna,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 323440.0,
      "end_time": 326900.0,
      "text": "you wanna taste the red meat, the akami."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 326900.0,
      "end_time": 329409.0,
      "text": "It's a wild animal, so it tells you whether"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 329410.0,
      "end_time": 330410.0,
      "text": "it had a good diet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 330410.0,
      "end_time": 331910.0,
      "text": "whether it had a good life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 331910.0,
      "end_time": 336240.0,
      "text": "and it got exercise, and it lived in clean waters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 336240.0,
      "end_time": 338700.0,
      "text": "and was able to swim around a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 338700.0,
      "end_time": 341810.0,
      "text": "So, a farm-raised tuna is, generally, force-fed sardines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 341810.0,
      "end_time": 343240.0,
      "text": "and you can actually taste sardines"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 343240.0,
      "end_time": 345780.0,
      "text": "in the fat of a farm-raised tuna."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 345780.0,
      "end_time": 348400.0,
      "text": "Whereas a wild tuna has a varied diet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 348400.0,
      "end_time": 351609.0,
      "text": "and has a much cleaner and milder flavor to the fat."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 351610.0,
      "end_time": 353670.0,
      "text": "Narrator: But for decades, wild bluefin tuna"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 353670.0,
      "end_time": 355700.0,
      "text": "were over-fished in the Pacific,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 355700.0,
      "end_time": 357300.0,
      "text": "which was harming their population"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 357300.0,
      "end_time": 359680.0,
      "text": "and making it more difficult to come by."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 359680.0,
      "end_time": 362970.0,
      "text": "However, more recently tighter controls on fishing"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 362970.0,
      "end_time": 365640.0,
      "text": "have led to a resurgence in the population."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 365640.0,
      "end_time": 367810.0,
      "text": "But they could still be better, Wilcox says."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 367810.0,
      "end_time": 370740.0,
      "text": "In fact, Wilcox avoids any Pacific bluefin"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 370740.0,
      "end_time": 372400.0,
      "text": "that is not from Japan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 372400.0,
      "end_time": 373770.0,
      "text": "and says you should too."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 373770.0,
      "end_time": 377940.0,
      "text": "Wilcox: If you eat Pacific bluefin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 377103.0,
      "end_time": 378836.0,
      "text": "not specifically from Japan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 378836.0,
      "end_time": 383403.0,
      "text": "then that's really irresponsible."
    }
  ]
}